PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?zipCode WHERE {
  ?entity wdt:P131 wd:Q5083 .
  ?entity wdt:P281 ?zipCode .
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?coordinates ?continent ?neighboringCountry WHERE {
  wd:Q783 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
  wd:Q783 wdt:P30 ?continent .
  wd:Q783 wdt:P47 ?neighboringCountry .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country WHERE {
  wd:Q1215310 wdt:P276 ?location .
  ?location wdt:P131 * ?country .
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2013-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= '2013-01-01' ^^ xsd:date ) .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?vicePresident WHERE {
  wd:Q1124 p:P39 ?presidentStatement .
  ?presidentStatement ps:P39 ?presidentPosition .
  ?presidentPosition wdt:P361 ?administration .
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?vicePresidentStatement .
  ?vicePresidentStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?vicePresidentStatement pq:P361 ?administration .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q91 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?series ?year ?winner WHERE {
  ?series wdt:P118 wd:Q1215892 .
  ?series wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 .
  ?series wdt:P585 ?date .
  ?series wdt:P1346 ?winner .
  FILTER ( ?winner = wd:Q203008 ) BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?county ?coordinates ?city WHERE {
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P131 ?county .
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P276 ?city .
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?movie ?character WHERE {
  VALUES ?movie {
    wd:Q181795 wd:Q181803
  }
  .
  ?movie wdt:P161 wd:Q358345 .
  ?movie p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P161 wd:Q358345 ; pq:P453 ?character .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?birthName ?occupation ?gender ?birthDate ?citizenship ?birthPlace ?deathDate WHERE {
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P735 ?birthName .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P106 ?occupation .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P21 ?gender .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P569 ?birthDate .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P27 ?citizenship .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P19 ?birthPlace .
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P570 ?deathDate .
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?vicePresident WHERE {
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '1961-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '1963-11-22T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q6583 wdt:P17 ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?primeMinister ?primeMinisterLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q29 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?primeMinister .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?primeMinister rdfs:label ?primeMinisterLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?primeMinisterLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?team ?award WHERE {
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P54 ?team .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P166 ?award .
  FILTER ( ?team IN ( wd:Q128109 , wd:Q161345 , wd:Q167253 ) ) .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q213081 p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P161 ?actor ; pq:P453 wd:Q119138548 .
}
